doc.previous: In January 2014 EADS was reorganised as Airbus Group with three divisions Airbus Airbus Defence and Space and Airbus Helicopters 3  On 31 July 2013 it was reported that EADS was to be renamed in 2014 to Airbus Group adopting the name of its commercial aircraft building subsidiary 37
